                                    >
                                        Transition safely out of your boot. Take
                                        your first confident steps. Improve
                                        balance and proprioception. Begin early
                                        strengthening exercises.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="hidden md:block left-1/2 absolute -translate-x-1/2"
