                                        Explosive Power & Plyometrics
                                    </h3>
                                    <p
                                        class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
                                    >
                                        Develop explosive strength through
                                        advanced training. Master plyometric
                                        exercises. Prepare for full return to
                                        competitive sports and high-intensity
                                        activities.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div
